data.title: AZCO
data.meta_description: AZCO is a wholly owned subsidiary of Burns & McDonnell. We are 100% employee-owned, with more than 180 employees working with over 750 experienced union craft personnel.
data.text:
Safe, Predictable, High-Quality Construction

We work with union craft labor across the country in markets ranging from renewable energy to manufacturing to pipelines. As part of the Burns & McDonnell family of companies, we can leverage the resources of a world-class engineering firm to bring you solutions tailored to your needs, from integrated engineer-procure-construct (EPC) and design-build to prefabrication/construction-only.

Cobots: Bringing Innovation

When cobots take on the everyday, it frees our craft and craft hours for doing the more complex welds that make our fabrication shop more valuable to our projects.

Shop manager Eric Bestul discusses the benefits of having a cobot in the shop, including making our work faster and more efficient.

Learn More About Our Shops
